### Framework 16 Hardware Key Mappings
### Volume Controls (F1-F3)
bindsym XF86AudioMute exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-volume.bb mute
bindsym XF86AudioLowerVolume exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-volume.bb down
bindsym XF86AudioRaiseVolume exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-volume.bb up

### Brightness Controls (F7-F8)
bindsym XF86MonBrightnessDown exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-brightness.bb down
bindsym XF86MonBrightnessUp exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-brightness.bb up

### WiFi Controls (F9-F12)
bindsym XF86WLAN exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb status
bindsym XF86Bluetooth exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb switch-starlink
bindsym XF86RFKill exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb switch-cellular

### Additional Framework 16 Keys
bindsym XF86TouchpadToggle exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-touchpad.bb toggle
bindsym XF86Display exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/framework16-display.bb cycle

### Dual WiFi Manager Integration
bindsym $mod+Shift+w exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb start
bindsym $mod+Alt+w exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb status
bindsym $mod+Control+w exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb switch-starlink
bindsym $mod+Shift+Control+w exec bb /home/xy/kae3g/12025-10/scripts/dual-wifi-manager.bb switch-cellular
